<font color="yellow">I guess...</font>

87
00:08:22,900 --> 00:08:24,940
<font color="yellow">this is where it ends for us.</font>

88
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:29,470
<font color="yellow">But still,</font>

89
00:08:30,440 --> 00:08:31,870
