<font color="yellow">I'm glad...</font>

93
00:08:39,570 --> 00:08:40,970
<font color="yellow">I got to see you.</font>

94
00:08:42,770 --> 00:08:45,150
<font color="yellow">Yes, take care.</font>

95
00:08:45,150 --> 00:08:47,700
<font color="yellow">Look after your looks so that...</font>

96
00:08:49,270 --> 00:08:51,600
