97
00:08:52,540 --> 00:08:53,540
<font color="yellow">Okay?</font>

98
00:08:56,270 --> 00:08:59,800
<font color="yellow">Yes. I have to go to my friend now.</font>

99
00:09:02,300 --> 00:09:03,340
<font color="yellow">Bye.</font>

100
00:09:28,570 --> 00:09:30,700
<font color="yellow">Why do you keep calling me?</font>

101
00:09:31,640 --> 00:09:32,670
<font color="yellow">Where are you?</font>

102
