<font color="yellow">Tell me where you are!</font>

103
00:09:44,740 --> 00:09:46,770
<font color="yellow">This will be our last time, right?</font>

104
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:52,740
<font color="yellow">I should've told her I got divorced.</font>

105
00:09:56,070 --> 00:09:57,070
<font color="yellow">Will you...</font>

106
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:59,270
<font color="yellow">tell her...</font>

107
00:10:00,770 --> 00:10:03,500
<font color="yellow">after I'm dead and gone?</font>

108
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:06,170
<font color="yellow">That I got divorced...</font>

109
00:10:07,670 --> 00:10:08,910
<font color="yellow">and loved her.</font>

110
00:10:12,970 --> 00:10:14,040
<font color="yellow">Only her.</font>

111
00:10:37,540 --> 00:10:38,770
<font color="yellow">Where's my key?</font>

112
00:10:52,970 --> 00:10:55,330
