117
00:11:04,870 --> 00:11:06,040
<font color="yellow">Where are you going?</font>

118
00:11:06,900 --> 00:11:08,800
<font color="yellow">He's helpless.</font>

119
00:11:15,040 --> 00:11:17,940
<font color="yellow">How do I know which road Hee Ja takes?</font>

120
00:11:19,070 --> 00:11:20,170
<font color="yellow">My goodness.</font>

