<font color="yellow">Yes, I am.</font>

124
00:11:27,700 --> 00:11:30,040
<font color="yellow">But how would I know what route...</font>

125
00:11:30,040 --> 00:11:32,070
<font color="yellow">Hee Ja takes from our house to hers?</font>

126
00:11:32,070 --> 00:11:34,540
<font color="yellow">Take the road by Bisan Hill.</font>

127
00:11:34,540 --> 00:11:36,870
<font color="yellow">Jeong A says Hee Ja takes that road.</font>

128
00:11:36,870 --> 00:11:39,070
<font color="yellow">Okay. Wait, Seong Jae.</font>

129
00:11:39,900 --> 00:11:42,880
<font color="yellow">Are you sure she has dementia?</font>

130
00:11:42,880 --> 00:11:47,570
<font color="yellow">I was thinking. She's always been a bit weird.</font>

131
00:11:47,570 --> 00:11:48,900
