134
00:11:55,770 --> 00:11:57,830
<font color="yellow">(Seong Jae)</font>

135
00:11:57,830 --> 00:11:59,600
<font color="yellow">When did he hang up?</font>

136
00:12:53,970 --> 00:12:55,100
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

137
00:12:56,040 --> 00:12:57,540
<font color="yellow">Yes, thank you.</font>

138
00:12:57,540 --> 00:13:00,440
<font color="yellow">I'll come over, then. Bye.</font>

139
00:13:05,470 --> 00:13:06,840
<font color="yellow">Yes, it's me.</font>

140
00:13:08,200 --> 00:13:11,000
