<font color="yellow">I called Nan Hee's restaurant.</font>

146
00:13:25,190 --> 00:13:27,810
<font color="yellow">The employee said Hee Ja didn't come by.</font>

147
00:13:27,810 --> 00:13:29,530
<font color="yellow">She was at church.</font>

148
