<font color="yellow">I'm going to visit the church.</font>

158
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:00,900
<font color="yellow">I can't just sit around.</font>

159
00:14:02,370 --> 00:14:03,440
<font color="yellow">Sit back down.</font>

