<font color="yellow">She gets things delivered.</font>

175
00:15:38,140 --> 00:15:40,040
<font color="yellow">What's the point of staring at each other in the face?</font>

176
00:15:40,040 --> 00:15:41,300
<font color="yellow">We'll only be annoyed.</font>

177
00:15:41,900 --> 00:15:43,000
<font color="yellow">You're right.</font>

178
00:15:44,840 --> 00:15:47,740
<font color="yellow">I'm so upset that Hee Ja's head...</font>

179
00:15:47,740 --> 00:15:48,970
<font color="yellow">is so messy like this.</font>

180
00:15:49,300 --> 00:15:50,830
<font color="yellow">Don't talk.</font>

181
00:15:50,830 --> 00:15:52,140
<font color="yellow">Just clean.</font>

182
00:16:26,200 --> 00:16:27,200
<font color="yellow">Yes, Ha Neul.</font>

183
00:16:29,900 --> 00:16:32,450
<font color="yellow">It's okay. Her friends and her boyfriend is here.</font>

184
00:16:32,450 --> 00:16:33,470
<font color="yellow">The lawyer guy.</font>

185
00:16:34,470 --> 00:16:36,540
<font color="yellow">Yes. He's running around to sort it out.</font>

186
00:16:38,470 --> 00:16:39,800
<font color="yellow">Of course, I'm fine.</font>

187
00:16:42,970 --> 00:16:43,970
<font color="yellow">Ha Neul,</font>

188
00:16:44,670 --> 00:16:46,670
<font color="yellow">don't stress yourself. You should be careful.</font>

189
00:16:49,170 --> 00:16:50,570
<font color="yellow">I'm fine.</font>

190
00:16:51,170 --> 00:16:54,240
<font color="yellow">That's what you should do for Mum, okay?</font>

191
00:16:56,170 --> 00:16:57,350
<font color="yellow">I know.</font>

