00:17:50,240 --> 00:17:52,630
<font color="yellow">from Nan Hee's restaurant to Hee Ja's place.</font>

201
00:17:52,630 --> 00:17:54,000
<font color="yellow">What difference will that...</font>

202
00:17:55,770 --> 00:17:56,770
<font color="yellow">Anyway,</font>

