214
00:19:07,340 --> 00:19:09,500
<font color="yellow">like this while enjoying it.</font>

215
00:19:10,400 --> 00:19:11,400
<font color="yellow">It's all ruined.</font>

216
00:19:12,200 --> 00:19:13,300
<font color="yellow">It's messed up.</font>

