00:20:48,970 --> 00:20:50,170
<font color="yellow">I can't drive.</font>

242
00:20:50,640 --> 00:20:52,500
<font color="yellow">You had one shot.</font>

243
00:20:53,870 --> 00:20:55,070
<font color="yellow">Are you scared of dying?</font>

244
00:20:56,200 --> 00:20:58,940
<font color="yellow">I think I'm struggling to live.</font>

245
00:21:01,240 --> 00:21:02,770
<font color="yellow">That's the same thing.</font>

246
00:21:06,470 --> 00:21:08,500
<font color="yellow">Do you want me to tell Wan?</font>

247
00:21:10,000 --> 00:21:11,070
<font color="yellow">Or do you want to tell her?</font>

248
00:21:12,000 --> 00:21:13,670
<font color="yellow">Do whatever you want.</font>

249
00:21:13,670 --> 00:21:15,500
<font color="yellow">It doesn't matter who tells her.</font>

250
00:21:15,500 --> 00:21:16,870
<font color="yellow">It's the same thing.</font>

251
00:21:20,470 --> 00:21:21,540
<font color="yellow">I'll do it then.</font>

252
00:21:25,040 --> 00:21:26,870
<font color="yellow">Your hands are still so beautiful.</font>

253
00:21:28,770 --> 00:21:31,540
<font color="yellow">It's not just my hands. My body is pretty hot.</font>

254
00:21:32,610 --> 00:21:33,970
<font color="yellow">Who cares?</font>

255
00:21:34,570 --> 00:21:36,000
<font color="yellow">No one is there to touch it.</font>

256
00:21:36,570 --> 00:21:39,700
<font color="yellow">We both have it bad.</font>

257
00:21:42,300 --> 00:21:44,740
<font color="yellow">It's really ruined.</font>

258
00:21:45,500 --> 00:21:46,500
<font color="yellow">My life's ruined.</font>

259
00:21:48,040 --> 00:21:50,600
<font color="yellow">I tried to live nobly as a good wife, a good mother...</font>

260
00:21:51,070 --> 00:21:52,140
<font color="yellow">and a good daughter.</font>

261
00:21:52,840 --> 00:21:54,770
<font color="yellow">I acted like I was strong.</font>

262
00:21:57,270 --> 00:21:59,970
<font color="yellow">This is such a shame.</font>

263
00:21:59,970 --> 00:22:01,390
<font color="yellow">If I knew this would happen...</font>

264
00:22:01,390 --> 00:22:04,270
<font color="yellow">We should have just slept with any and every guy.</font>

265
00:22:06,840 --> 00:22:09,700
