266
00:22:10,940 --> 00:22:13,340
<font color="yellow">Watch your mouth.</font>

267
00:22:14,700 --> 00:22:17,930
<font color="yellow">Even if we tell them,</font>

268
00:22:17,930 --> 00:22:19,670
<font color="yellow">no one would line up.</font>

269
00:22:20,100 --> 00:22:22,140
<font color="yellow">No way.</font>

270
00:22:30,300 --> 00:22:32,270
<font color="yellow">We're ruined.</font>

271
00:22:43,270 --> 00:22:44,270
<font color="yellow">Yeong Won.</font>

272
00:22:45,670 --> 00:22:47,440
<font color="yellow">When you got your first surgery...</font>

273
00:22:48,440 --> 00:22:49,440
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

274
00:22:50,340 --> 00:22:52,200
<font color="yellow">When you first heard the news,</font>

