00:22:58,770 --> 00:23:00,370
<font color="yellow">It was horrible.</font>

277
00:23:01,300 --> 00:23:04,050
<font color="yellow">Then was the second time horrific?</font>

278
00:23:04,050 --> 00:23:06,340
<font color="yellow">The third time was horrendous.</font>

279
00:23:08,440 --> 00:23:10,300
<font color="yellow">That's enough.</font>

280
00:23:13,240 --> 00:23:15,070
<font color="yellow">Look who's talking.</font>

281
00:23:15,070 --> 00:23:18,300
<font color="yellow">You little piece of...</font>

282
00:24:24,700 --> 00:24:25,700
<font color="yellow">Wan.</font>

283
00:24:26,470 --> 00:24:27,600
<font color="yellow">Where are you?</font>

284
00:25:02,730 --> 00:25:04,230
<font color="yellow">Why are you looking down?</font>

285
00:25:06,290 --> 00:25:08,960
<font color="yellow">Because I'm that frustrated.</font>

286
00:25:11,390 --> 00:25:12,860
<font color="yellow">She wouldn't have jumped.</font>

287
00:25:14,290 --> 00:25:16,260
<font color="yellow">She has that much sense in her.</font>

288
00:25:17,490 --> 00:25:18,490
<font color="yellow">Dementia...</font>

289
00:25:19,090 --> 00:25:20,090
<font color="yellow">doesn't come suddenly.</font>

290
00:25:21,230 --> 00:25:22,360
<font color="yellow">It progresses slowly.</font>

291
00:25:23,290 --> 00:25:25,730
<font color="yellow">My mother had dementia, remember?</font>

292
00:25:27,930 --> 00:25:29,890
<font color="yellow">Didn't your mother have it, too?</font>

293
00:25:30,790 --> 00:25:32,760
<font color="yellow">My mum died on the street.</font>

294
00:25:33,760 --> 00:25:36,290
<font color="yellow">There was no medication for it back then.</font>

295
00:25:40,230 --> 00:25:43,160
<font color="yellow">That's the first time you said something sensible.</font>

296
00:25:43,160 --> 00:25:44,630
<font color="yellow">Where are your manners?</font>

297
00:25:46,190 --> 00:25:48,860
<font color="yellow">Are you memorising the ten rules of a good husband?</font>

298
00:25:49,590 --> 00:25:51,030
<font color="yellow">What's the first one?</font>

299
00:25:51,560 --> 00:25:52,590
<font color="yellow">"A husband..."</font>

300
00:25:54,290 --> 00:25:57,060
<font color="yellow">"should not vent his frustration or anger from work..."</font>

301
00:25:57,060 --> 00:25:58,660
<font color="yellow">"on his family at home."</font>

302
00:25:59,890 --> 00:26:00,990
<font color="yellow">You're doing well.</font>

303
00:26:02,390 --> 00:26:04,190
<font color="yellow">Be good to Jeong A.</font>

304
00:26:04,690 --> 00:26:05,860
<font color="yellow">Look at Hee Ja.</font>

305
00:26:08,090 --> 00:26:09,560
<font color="yellow">One by one,</font>

306
00:26:10,060 --> 00:26:11,330
<font color="yellow">we'll all die.</font>

307
00:26:15,290 --> 00:26:17,660
<font color="yellow">Get in. Let's try another bridge.</font>

308
00:26:34,490 --> 00:26:36,990
<font color="yellow">Come on. Eat up.</font>

309
00:26:37,390 --> 00:26:38,390
<font color="yellow">No thanks.</font>

