00:26:40,430 --> 00:26:42,400
<font color="yellow">It's cooked.</font>

311
00:26:42,400 --> 00:26:43,830
<font color="yellow">Don't waste food.</font>

312
00:26:53,490 --> 00:26:54,590
<font color="yellow">Did you...</font>

313
00:26:55,430 --> 00:26:56,430
<font color="yellow">tell your brothers?</font>

314
00:26:57,560 --> 00:26:58,830
<font color="yellow">Sort of.</font>

315
00:27:00,190 --> 00:27:01,260
<font color="yellow">So they wouldn't worry.</font>

316
00:27:03,090 --> 00:27:04,690
<font color="yellow">A sister-in-law has thyroid cancer.</font>

317
00:27:05,660 --> 00:27:07,030
<font color="yellow">I said I'd call back.</font>

318
00:27:08,760 --> 00:27:09,940
<font color="yellow">Drink up.</font>

319
00:27:09,940 --> 00:27:11,580
<font color="yellow">I'm fine. You have some.</font>

