00:27:11,580 --> 00:27:15,030
<font color="yellow">I can't. I have to drive.</font>

321
00:27:15,960 --> 00:27:16,960
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

322
00:27:24,490 --> 00:27:26,660
<font color="yellow">Your mother...</font>

323
00:27:28,390 --> 00:27:31,160
<font color="yellow">will be fine. I guarantee you.</font>

324
00:27:32,390 --> 00:27:35,030
<font color="yellow">If something terrible had happened,</font>

325
00:27:35,560 --> 00:27:37,760
<font color="yellow">we'd have gotten a call.</font>

326
00:27:37,760 --> 00:27:39,260
<font color="yellow">That's what happens.</font>

327
00:27:39,990 --> 00:27:43,190
<font color="yellow">We haven't heard from anyone, so nothing bad has happened.</font>

328
00:27:43,560 --> 00:27:47,910
<font color="yellow">I like and care for your mother very much,</font>

