00:27:49,910 --> 00:27:54,190
<font color="yellow">We need the strength to protect her.</font>

331
00:28:01,890 --> 00:28:04,760
<font color="yellow">Does my liking your mother...</font>

332
00:28:05,590 --> 00:28:06,860
<font color="yellow">bother you that much?</font>

333
00:28:08,330 --> 00:28:10,590
<font color="yellow">Even if it does, it can't be helped.</font>

334
00:28:11,290 --> 00:28:12,590
<font color="yellow">I like your mother...</font>

335
00:28:13,290 --> 00:28:14,990
<font color="yellow">a lot, you know?</font>

336
00:28:15,690 --> 00:28:18,160
<font color="yellow">But even so,</font>

337
00:28:19,090 --> 00:28:20,390
<font color="yellow">we're just friends.</font>

338
00:28:21,760 --> 00:28:23,060
<font color="yellow">Best friends.</font>

339
00:28:29,090 --> 00:28:30,130
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

340
00:28:32,360 --> 00:28:33,690
<font color="yellow">Now, talk less and eat more.</font>

341
00:28:34,390 --> 00:28:38,330
<font color="yellow">Eat up. A man should be confident and strong.</font>

342
00:28:38,860 --> 00:28:40,390
<font color="yellow">Eat up and cheer up.</font>

343
00:28:40,890 --> 00:28:42,390
<font color="yellow">- Okay?
-  Okay.</font>

344
00:28:47,660 --> 00:28:49,760
<font color="yellow">Hello? Yes, hi.</font>

345
00:28:50,430 --> 00:28:51,430
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

346
00:28:51,860 --> 00:28:52,960
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

347
00:28:53,590 --> 00:28:56,000
<font color="yellow">I was killing time...</font>

348
00:28:56,000 --> 00:28:59,210
<font color="yellow">at a nearby police station.</font>

349
00:28:59,210 --> 00:29:01,960
<font color="yellow">Okay, I'll be right there.</font>

350
00:29:02,760 --> 00:29:05,380
<font color="yellow">Stop eating. We have to go.</font>

351
00:29:05,380 --> 00:29:07,120
<font color="yellow">- They found your mum.
-  What?</font>

352
00:29:07,120 --> 00:29:09,000
<font color="yellow">Can we pay quickly?</font>

353
00:29:09,000 --> 00:29:11,130
<font color="yellow">Pack this up. We'll come back for it.</font>

354
00:29:11,690 --> 00:29:12,690
<font color="yellow">Thanks.</font>

355
00:29:21,760 --> 00:29:23,560
<font color="yellow">Hello, Mr Lee.</font>

356
00:29:25,060 --> 00:29:27,160
<font color="yellow">Did you find my friend?</font>

357
00:29:27,160 --> 00:29:28,990
<font color="yellow">Yes. Have a look at this.</font>

358
00:29:29,660 --> 00:29:33,260
<font color="yellow">I traced the person you sent a photo of.</font>

359
00:29:47,330 --> 00:29:48,330
<font color="yellow">That's her.</font>

360
00:29:49,790 --> 00:29:52,960
<font color="yellow">Isn't that Hangang Bridge?</font>

361
00:29:55,690 --> 00:29:58,660
<font color="yellow">What is she carrying on her back?</font>

362
00:30:31,730 --> 00:30:32,760
<font color="yellow">That's it.</font>

363
00:30:33,860 --> 00:30:34,960
<font color="yellow">We got too close today.</font>

364
00:30:35,290 --> 00:30:36,860
<font color="yellow">How's the novel coming along?</font>

365
00:30:37,660 --> 00:30:40,080
<font color="yellow">It's the first draft, but I'm 70 percent done.</font>

366
00:30:40,080 --> 00:30:42,160
<font color="yellow">Why did you call me? You should be working.</font>

367
00:30:43,060 --> 00:30:45,230
<font color="yellow">You're just delaying your departure date.</font>

368
00:30:45,560 --> 00:30:48,030
<font color="yellow">You sound like an evil boyfriend...</font>

369
00:30:48,030 --> 00:30:49,190
<font color="yellow">who abuses his lover.</font>

370
00:30:49,790 --> 00:30:53,480
<font color="yellow">I need breaks, too. I'm not a machine.</font>

371
00:30:53,480 --> 00:30:54,490
<font color="yellow">Here's your prize.</font>

372
00:30:55,190 --> 00:30:56,190
<font color="yellow">Have this.</font>

373
00:30:57,560 --> 00:30:59,630
<font color="yellow">- Do you want to die?
