374
00:31:08,260 --> 00:31:09,260
<font color="yellow">Here's your real prize.</font>

375
00:31:32,190 --> 00:31:33,190
<font color="yellow">What's that?</font>

376
00:31:33,690 --> 00:31:35,560
<font color="yellow">I'm holding myself up with my arms.</font>

377
00:31:36,790 --> 00:31:37,860
<font color="yellow">I can't use my legs yet.</font>

378
00:31:39,090 --> 00:31:41,760
<font color="yellow">But it's important to try.</font>

379
00:31:43,160 --> 00:31:44,490
<font color="yellow">I'm always scared of falling.</font>

