00:31:44,990 --> 00:31:47,630
<font color="yellow">I hadn't tried this, but I started recently.</font>

381
00:31:48,960 --> 00:31:49,960
<font color="yellow">For you.</font>

382
00:32:06,190 --> 00:32:07,190
<font color="yellow">Get back to work.</font>

383
00:32:11,930 --> 00:32:13,590
<font color="yellow">I can leave on this day.</font>

384
00:32:15,960 --> 00:32:17,130
<font color="yellow">I'm waiting.</font>

385
00:32:17,990 --> 00:32:19,190
<font color="yellow">(Off to see Yeon Ha!)</font>

386
00:32:21,690 --> 00:32:22,690
<font color="yellow">My arms hurt.</font>

387
00:32:23,330 --> 00:32:24,330
<font color="yellow">Let's hang up.</font>

388
00:32:28,090 --> 00:32:29,090
<font color="yellow">Hang up.</font>

389
00:32:51,260 --> 00:32:53,230
<font color="yellow">What? Yeong Won?</font>

390
00:32:56,860 --> 00:32:58,860
<font color="yellow">Yeong Won, what brings you here?</font>

391
00:33:01,960 --> 00:33:03,830
<font color="yellow">Why did you visit me?</font>

392
00:33:37,130 --> 00:33:40,190
<font color="yellow">The doctor that Mum saw...</font>

393
00:33:41,530 --> 00:33:43,790
<font color="yellow">Can I see him right now?</font>

394
00:33:54,860 --> 00:33:58,290
<font color="yellow">Dr Cho. I'm really sorry,</font>

395
00:33:58,890 --> 00:34:01,330
<font color="yellow">but could you meet with me right now?</font>

396
00:34:02,730 --> 00:34:04,230
<font color="yellow">You're available?</font>

397
00:34:07,460 --> 00:34:10,190
<font color="yellow">Okay, where should I go?</font>

398
00:34:12,030 --> 00:34:14,290
<font color="yellow">Okay. There?</font>

399
00:34:16,290 --> 00:34:17,290
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

400
00:34:27,960 --> 00:34:30,260
<font color="yellow">Your mum already knows.</font>

401
00:34:31,160 --> 00:34:34,560
<font color="yellow">She should know since it's her body.</font>

402
00:34:35,730 --> 00:34:38,130
<font color="yellow">You said earlier that...</font>

403
00:34:38,960 --> 00:34:42,760
<font color="yellow">60 to 70 percent of these people don't get surgery,</font>

404
00:34:43,390 --> 00:34:48,000
<font color="yellow">and the recovery rate with surgery is less than 20 percent...</font>

405
00:34:48,000 --> 00:34:50,780
<font color="yellow">Personally, I believe that they should get surgery...</font>

406
00:34:50,780 --> 00:34:52,360
<font color="yellow">if there's even a slightest chance.</font>

407
00:34:53,430 --> 00:34:56,130
<font color="yellow">20 percent is still a possibility.</font>

408
00:35:09,190 --> 00:35:12,060
<font color="yellow">That's what I wanted to hear. It's possible.</font>

409
00:35:13,560 --> 00:35:14,660
<font color="yellow">Thank you, Doctor.</font>

410
00:35:17,560 --> 00:35:18,930
<font color="yellow">I'm going to go.</font>

411
00:35:22,530 --> 00:35:25,960
<font color="yellow">Wan, I'll tell your grandmother.</font>

412
00:35:35,360 --> 00:35:36,360
<font color="yellow">Yes, Choong Nam.</font>

413
00:35:37,230 --> 00:35:39,230
<font color="yellow">Why didn't you pick up?</font>

414
00:35:40,360 --> 00:35:42,730
<font color="yellow">I know you are annoyed with us,</font>

415
00:35:43,060 --> 00:35:45,600
<font color="yellow">but we called because we can't get through to your mum.</font>

416
00:35:47,760 --> 00:35:48,760
<font color="yellow">Wan.</font>

417
00:35:50,130 --> 00:35:52,060
<font color="yellow">Hee Ja has dementia...</font>

418
00:35:52,760 --> 00:35:55,330
<font color="yellow">and she disappeared.</font>

419
00:35:56,160 --> 00:35:58,230
<font color="yellow">So tell your mum...</font>

420
00:36:00,930 --> 00:36:01,930
<font color="yellow">Choong Nam.</font>

421
00:36:04,100 --> 00:36:06,360
<font color="yellow">I can't tell my mum that right now.</font>

422
00:36:06,360 --> 00:36:08,490
<font color="yellow">So don't try calling her either.</font>

423
00:36:09,490 --> 00:36:10,730
<font color="yellow">She has cancer.</font>

424
00:36:23,690 --> 00:36:24,690
<font color="yellow">What is it?</font>

425
00:36:25,330 --> 00:36:26,530
<font color="yellow">What did Wan say?</font>

426
00:36:34,890 --> 00:36:36,960
<font color="yellow">Don't talk to me right now.</font>

427
00:36:37,990 --> 00:36:39,730
<font color="yellow">I'm dizzy.</font>

428
00:36:54,860 --> 00:36:56,690
<font color="yellow">What is this?</font>

429
00:37:10,190 --> 00:37:11,360
<font color="yellow">(Jeju Vegetable Store)</font>

430
00:37:16,330 --> 00:37:18,030
<font color="yellow">Jeju Vegetable Store?</font>

431
00:37:19,860 --> 00:37:22,130
<font color="yellow">Sorry to call you so late.</font>

432
00:37:22,130 --> 00:37:24,390
<font color="yellow">I don't think I can...</font>

433
00:37:25,100 --> 00:37:27,130
<font color="yellow">go to your store for a while.</font>

434
00:37:27,830 --> 00:37:29,730
<font color="yellow">I need your onions.</font>

435
00:37:29,730 --> 00:37:32,690
<font color="yellow">Can you prepare them for my restaurant and...</font>

436
00:37:40,990 --> 00:37:42,060
<font color="yellow">Hey.</font>

437
00:37:42,690 --> 00:37:45,360
<font color="yellow">My mum needs to get surgery.</font>

